SQL_STMT_U.val: SELECT T3.Descrip AS 'ALAT', T0.Dscription AS 'NAMA TINDAKAN', T1.DocDate AS 'TANGGAL', T4.CardName AS 'DOKTER', T1.NumAtCard AS 'NO PENDAFTARAN', T1.CardName AS 'NAMA PASIEN', Tx.CardName AS 'Penjamin', T0.Quantity AS 'QTY', T0.PriceBefDi AS 'HARGA', T0.Quantity * T0.PriceBefDi AS 'TOTAL' FROM INV1 (NOLOCK) T0 JOIN OINV T1 ON T0.DocEntry = T1.DocEntry AND T1.DocSubType = '--' LEFT JOIN OCRD Tx ON T1.BPChCode = Tx.CardCode LEFT JOIN OITM T2 ON T0.ItemCode = T2.ItemCode LEFT JOIN OSGP T3 ON T2.ServiceGrp = T3.AbsEntry LEFT JOIN OCRD T4 ON T0.VendorNum = T4.CardCode WHERE T1.CANCELED='n' AND (T1.TrackNo IS NOT NULL OR t1.TrackNo <> '') AND T1.DocDate BETWEEN :4 AND :5 AND (T3.Descrip = :1 or :1 is null or :1 = '') AND (T0.Dscription = :2 or :2 is null or :2 = '') AND ( CASE WHEN 'All' = :3 THEN 1 WHEN 'Y' = :3 AND T3.Descrip IS NOT NULL THEN 1 WHEN 'N' = :3 AND T3.Descrip IS NULL THEN 1 ELSE 0 END = 1 ) ORDER BY CASE WHEN T3.Descrip IS NOT NULL THEN 0 ELSE 1 END, T3.Descrip ASC
